<font color="#FF0000">REAL MEN ARE NOT HYENA'S</font><br>
<tt>Tue Sep  9 23:36:12 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
Hey Hyena Pack, you are so easily fooled by the old lion. Finally, when the lion is too old, or too weary, to fend off your constant nips, can you conquer and kill the majesty beast. Before that happens, the majestic lion kills you one by one, until he is so weary, that the pack finally overcomes him.  This is the law of nature and Africa.  Not this site.<br><br>
I wrote the &quot;anon&quot; post about death, riding a pale horse (real original, I was watching Clint Eastwood at the time), and you all rallied around this &quot;vet thing&quot;.  What a laugh I had.<br><br>
I stood in a trench, once upon a time, in 1967, with an Uzi in my hands, trembling, looking out at Jordan. Two days later a friend said climb in, to his jeep, and off to the Negev we went to see the melted egyptian army. Yes Cook, I know about Israel. More than you can ever imagine. First hand, up close and personal. Even spent time with Moshe Dayan, if you know who he is.<br><br>
In my professional capacity, I helped over at least 400 police officers, almost all Vietnam vets, get out of the system. They were just burned out and needed to get out before they were killed off. I consider that a badge of bravery as well. They were mostly all vets, having traded one uniform for another in the 70's.<br><br>
I have locked and loaded with the best of them, qualified on almost every gun range, and the lamest of them is also my friend, but that is not good enough to overcome the rudeness that this site did to VietSon or Richard. <br><br>
Two voices from other viewpoints, one from Canada, one from Asia, both rudely put down by hyena's who only believe in magic indian words and rotor talk.  Bullshit talk, by boy scouts who are not men. Real men accept and listen to the voice of all, even those who are the enemy, or opposed to their point of view.  Cook has yet to answer one question that I have thrown to him, but he is quick to throw shit on me, i.e. The Little Commie.  Well, stupid is as stupid does.<br><br>
When you, the Hyena Pack, can bring back the women who used to post here, as well as the other points of view, then you will be warriors and men of honor. Until then, you are school yard bullys, and you deserve nothing, no respect, no acknowledgement, nothing. Keep your magic words and decoder rings to yourselfs, keep your word salad too yoursleves, real men don't need that kind of bullshit.  <br><br>
Real men, Real Warriors, real War Survivors, know that to talk, to share, to learn, and to heal, is enough.  Real men do not need to be in a pack of scavengers.
<p><code>-- In your face, and your gut, and heart,  (Dr. Barry C. Spatz) </code><p>


